body: Hi Olivier, That was a bug which is fixed now. If you update butterfly again you should be able to read the results to Grasshopper. [](http://api.ning.com:80/files/J17TP1ZnHTeS09BS*kolBXq2H8sKFlzJZVMGGhj*QQSSEF*T7uo6JqmsWn5C22ummNZ3abEqRbYFMAiGRGDWFOK9s2QLVEPT/probes_1.png) The results of your analysis doesn't look right. What is the Rhino units in your model. I guess you're using millimeters and not meters? Right now butterfly assumes that the units are set in meters. We should add unit conversation to butterfly.
